					 <strong>4 ways to Speed up your Metabolism</strong><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>How to speed up your metabolism?</span></figcaption></figure><p><span></span></p><p><span><b>Metabolism is an exchange of substances in our body, the speed of which depends on many factors.</b></span></p><p><span><i>Nutrition, physical activity, diseases and even climate, in particular it can have an effect on your metabolism.</i></span></p><ul><div><div></div></div><li><span><u><b>But what role does metabolism play in General?</b></u></span></li></ul><p><span>If you want to lose weight, or gain exactly muscle mass, then without a good metabolism to do it will be problematic.</span></p><blockquote><span>So now I will tell you about 4 ways, by observing these rules, you can easily increase your metabolic rate.</span></blockquote><h2><span>1. Drinking regime</span></h2><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>4 ways to Speed up your Metabolism</span></figcaption></figure><p><span></span></p><p><span>Water accelerates the metabolism by 3%. </span></p><p><span><i>But do not think that the figure is too small, it will already be perceptibly.</i></span></p><p><span><b>The daily norm of a person per day is 20 ml per kilogram of actual weight.</b></span></p><p><span>Here it is not difficult for everyone to calculate for themselves.</span></p><blockquote><span>Personally, I use an app on my smartphone, which automatically calculates the desired amount of liquid, and allows you to monitor the level of fluid throughout the day of drinks consumed.</span></blockquote><h2><span>2. Fractional power supply</span></h2><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Good nutrition</span></figcaption></figure><p><span></span></p><p><span><b>We often eat more than is necessary for life, because of this and many problems, such as excess weight or some diseases.</b></span></p><ul><li><span>Fractional nutrition, this is when we eat 4-6 once a day, but in small portions.</span></li></ul><p><span><i>This accelerates our metabolism, and also does not allow us to eat too much, since we are almost always full.</i></span></p><p><span>In addition to all this, we will have less stretching of the stomach, that is, the stomach will not bulge forward, and this is also important for the figure.</span></p><h2><span>3. Add to your diet protein</span></h2><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Diet for weight loss</span></figcaption></figure><p><span></span></p><p><span>Lean protein in the body accelerates the metabolism.</span></p><p><span><b>This happens because the body uses 2 times more calories to process it.</b></span></p><p><span><i>Also, it is important for those who want to lose weight, better stick to a protein diet, so with the same number of calories, the result will be better.</i></span></p><ul><li><span>The fact is that protein is the building material for muscles, and if there is a shortage of calories, there will be little protein, then on an equal basis with fat, the muscles will also go.</span></li></ul><h2><span>4. Sleep</span></h2><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Healthy sleep</span></figcaption></figure><blockquote><span>For the normal functioning of the body, recovery is necessary, and there is no better rest than sleep.</span></blockquote><p><span><b>A person needs 7-8 hours of sleep on average.</b></span></p><p><span><i>You need to remember that if you don't sleep the right amount it will be impossible to increase your metabolism.</i></span></p><ul><li><span>The same applies to losing weight and gaining muscle mass.</span></li></ul><p><span><b>Apply these techniques to practice, and you will have a normal metabolism, which will benefit the body.</b></span></p><p><span><u><i><b>I wish you all good luck!!!</b></i></u></span></p><blockquote><span>And if you are interested in the topic health and improvement of your body, then</span><span></span><a><b>SUBSCRIBE TO MY CHANNEL.</b></a></blockquote><p><span></span></p><p><span></span></p><div></div>
					
